menu.itemDescription: Look who's here - THE burger to rule them all. A real meaty flame-grilled Whopper® beef patty, topped with tangy pickles, ketchup, fresh tomatoes, crisp lettuce and fresh onions, finished with creamy mayo , and served on a toasted 5 sesame seed bun. Feeling hungry for a real meaty burger yet?
What else can we say, all the great taste of the WHOPPER® with cheese. A truly cheesillicious WHOPPIN' Time.

The same big WHOPPER® taste, but in a regular size. A mouth-watering, flame-grilled beef patty topped with fresh tomatoes, crisp lettuce, tangy pickles and crunchy onions, served on a toasted sesame seed bun and flavored with creamy mayo and ketchup. Ummm...yummy.
Double it up...Double the taste!! Grab hold of our Double BBQ Beefacon™ with cheese slices, Beefacon™ and delicious smokey BBQ sauce to complete the sensational taste.

Can't get enough of that heavenly creamy taste? Go for double the goodness! Melted Swiss cheese on two flame-grilled beef patties, topped with BK's special mushroom sauce, served on a sesame seed bun. Twice the velvety goodness in every bite.

Make room for our Double Cheeseburger, two signature flame-grilled beef patties topped with a simple layer of melted American cheese, crinkle cut pickles, yellow mustard, and ketchup on a toasted sesame seed bun.
Wonder why it’s called Tendergrill™? That’s ‘cos we made sure to flame-grill the chicken thighs to soft, juicy perfection. Best enjoyed with fries and soft drink.
Great selection of drinks to be consumed with or without straw. Your favourite drinks only @ BK. Choose your pleasure.
Makes mornings worth waking up for. Espresso and milk.
Enjoy it either Hot or Cold. You can never go wrong with the taste of Cocoa, giving you the energy you deserve!
Cool down with our Mineral water, it sure does quench your thirst!
Sweet taro chunks in a crispy pie crust. It'll win you over in a bite! Perfect after meals.
Sweet pineapple chunks in a crispy pie crust. It'll win you over in a bite! Perfect after meals.
There's more to sides than fries. Just ask fans of our famous Onion Rings, bursting with refreshing onion goodness inside! Perfect snack on its own or with a meal.
Something light on the tummy but super packed with great nutrients. Come enjoy our salad bowl with special sauce on its own or swap it with fries when you order your next BK meal!
Yummy shoe-string fires fried to a crisp golden brown, served piping hot withyour favourite Value Meal, or as the star of the moment.

menu.itemDescription: Wake up to BK’s classic crispy chicken fillet, fluffy eggs, delicious cheese and signature mushroom sauce together inside a fluffy, buttery CROISSAN’WICH® bun to bring you to cloud nine in one bite!
Kickstart the day with a sweet and savoury masterpiece!Our Cheesy Caramelized Onion Croissan'wich® is perfect for cheese lovers, and great for satisfying that morning hunger.

This signature combination of creamy mayo, Beefacon™, fluffy eggs and American cheese sandwiched between a CROISSAN’WICH® bun is sure to hit all the right spots if you’re looking for a savoury pick-me-up.
This sensational chicken strips, egg and cheese sauce sandwiched between soft buttery CROISSAN’WICH® is sure to tantalize your taste buds.
